        ♧t1♣
        ♤
          ♧type♣◇textView◆
          ♧text♣◇<div class="tv-article"><p class="tv-lead">The future of interface design lies not in complexity, but in the precise removal of everything unnecessary.</p><p>Good typography is the foundation of readable, accessible interfaces. It guides the eye, establishes hierarchy, and creates <strong>emotional resonance</strong> before a single word is consciously processed.</p><div class="tv-quote"><p>&quot;Design is not just what it looks like and feels like. Design is how it works.&quot;</p><cite>&mdash; Steve Jobs, 2003</cite></div><p>Learn more about <a href="#">typographic systems</a> and how to apply them with <em>intentionality and craft</em> in modern product design.</p></div>◆
