        ♧trunc♣
        ♤
          ♧type♣◇textView◆
          ♧text♣◇Product design is the process of identifying a market opportunity, clearly defining the problem, developing a proper solution for that problem and validating the solution with real users. It combines <span class="tv-highlight">UX research</span>, visual design, and engineering to create products that are both functional and delightful. A skilled product designer bridges the gap between user needs and business objectives, ensuring every decision is grounded in data and empathy.◆
