        ♤
          ♧type♣◇textView◆
          ♧text♣◇<ul class="tv-list"><li>Define the problem clearly before jumping to solutions</li><li>Prototype early and iterate based on user feedback</li><li>Measure success with both qualitative and quantitative data</li><li>Collaborate with engineers from day one, not after handoff</li><li>Prioritize accessibility as a core feature, not an afterthought</li></ul>◆
